NOTES_ON_ACTION_TAKEN: Derivation is: aleluj-a (shortening) > aleloj-a (affection) > aleloj-a (apocope) > alele: (monophthongization) > alle: (syncope + pal) > alle (reduction in unstressed syllable
column7: long-->short). This fix may not work allelu:j and alle still look to be related by chopping off syllable but this obscured crucial parts of the derivation. Note this is originally a Hebrew word. Remove?
